## Step 4: Connect Frontend ↔ Backend

### 4.1 Update Railway CORS
Go to Railway → `sms_backend` service → Variables. Update:
```
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://school-saas-frontend.vercel.app
```

### 4.2 Update Paystack Callback
If using Paystack, update:
```
PAYSTACK_CALLBACK_URL=https://school-saas-frontend.vercel.app/payments/verify
```

### 4.3 Redeploy Backend
Railway auto-redeploys when variables change.

