## Post-Deployment: Custom Domain (Optional)

### Backend (Railway)
```
Settings → Domains → Generate Domain
or
Settings → Domains → Add Custom Domain → api.yourschoolsaas.ng
```

### Frontend (Vercel)
```
Settings → Domains → Add Domain → app.yourschoolsaas.ng
```

Then update `CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` and `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` accordingly.

