## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| Railway build fails | Check logs. Ensure `Dockerfile` uses `mvn` not `./mvnw`. Verify `pom.xml` exists. |
| Vercel build fails | Check `package.json` exists. Ensure `npm ci` works locally. |
| CORS errors | Update `CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` in Railway with exact Vercel domain. |
| Paystack payments fail | Verify `PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY` is `sk_test_` (test) or `sk_live_` (production). Check callback URL. |
| Database connection fails | Verify `DATABASE_URL` is auto-injected by Railway PostgreSQL. |

